The paper focuses on load balancing in data center networks, which is a topic related to network infrastructure (NI) and software-defined networking (SD). The paper also discusses the impact of load balancing on flow completion time (DC) and proposes a new load balancing solution (CR). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of SDN (IT) to implement the proposed solution.
